{"tid":2282972,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子查七車牌被落案控告 當中至少五輛或為警方私家車","createTime":"2020-11-12T08:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-12T09:33:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"97adb539f23247fdeb1be811e6d6f43df17239f9","tid":2282972,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:37:17.000Z","msg":"繼《鏗鏘集》編導因車輛查冊被拘控後，警方再落案控告一名今年8月被捕的自僱男子，指他涉嫌查車牌時虛報用途，並且未經同意披露車主資料。自僱男被控八罪，今午在屯門裁判法院提堂。據控罪資料，七輛被查車輛當中，至少有五輛據報屬於警方或警務人員的私家車；其中一輛屬於現職警長，而該警長被指曾於今年八月跟蹤黃之鋒。案件押後再訊。<br />\n<br />\n根據控罪詳情並翻查《蘋果》資料，顯示遭披露車主身份的兩人，其中一人相信是一名警長；另一人則涉嫌瘋狂駕駛，切線兼撞向曾與他爭執的人。據了解，除了其中兩輛車未知詳情外，案中其餘五車輛均為警方使用。<br />\n<br />\n翻查以往報道，上述警長涉嫌今年8月駕車跟蹤及滋擾黃之鋒。至於涉及瘋狂駕駛的司機，則被拍下駕車撞人後，踩油加速推行傷者數十米，當時一度有指司機疑是警務人員。<br />\n<br />\n法庭應辯方要求，押後答辯，讓被告尋找律師、索取檢控文件及徵詢法律意見。署理主任裁判官張潔宜批准被告繼續以一萬元保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/BY4EMWMRMVEEBLQMAMMSH52JBE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2FBY4EMWMRMVEEBLQMAMMSH52JBE%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=014623dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201112%2FBY4EMWMRMVEEBLQMAMMSH52JBE%2F&h=0ff9d3a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201112/BY4EMWMRMVEEBLQMAMMSH52JBE/</a>"},{"pid":"d02b18e9dc428a1aeb99ddc55e54598d65f89294","tid":2282972,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:38:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e46e5a4e0ba79bd739a727ce76ce7a7b052cca9","tid":2282972,"uid":34410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d02b18e9dc428a1aeb99ddc55e54598d65f89294","tid":2282972,"uid":231583,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:38:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"張潔宜3隻字都知咩事"},{"pid":"fc1b7ce6865157e83a9b6cb2ef69a7c213653285","tid":2282972,"uid":113000,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:00:34.000Z","msg":"依家真係明屈<br />\n<br />\n公義已經永遠係香港失去"},{"pid":"218d31b076d137bf748b1eb08bfea9b178ea62e3","tid":2282972,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c66fa881927525a0a46ed783c1ff353b0c92ba","tid":2282972,"uid":240948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:04:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da2d8c7027d3f5932c9cb25c58924e44a7fd196","tid":2282972,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T09:07:05.000Z","msg":"被捕男子自從去年 6 月起受他人指使，在運輸署網上申請「車輛登記細節證明書」系統，申請超過1200份證明書。在申請過程中，他訛稱所獲取的證明書是用作法律訴訟及買賣車輛用途。證明書上面載有不同的個人資料，包括車牌號碼、車輛登記資料、車主姓名、住址、身份證號碼等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E8%BB%8A%E7%89%8C%E6%9F%A5%E5%86%8A%E8%B3%87%E6%96%99%E4%BB%A5-%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-%E7%AD%89-%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E6%BC%A2%E9%81%AD%E6%8E%A7-8-%E7%BD%AA%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2594%25AE%25E8%25BB%258A%25E7%2589%258C%25E6%259F%25A5%25E5%2586%258A%25E8%25B3%2587%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BB%25A5-%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%25BA%2595-%25E7%25AD%2589-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E9%2581%25AD%25E6%258E%25A7-8-%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%2F&d=J6hOlXozLSF63%2FYIn%2B2Au8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=fb7a03df\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2